NAME
      bal connector sdk - Generate and maintain Ballerina connectors from Java
       SDKs.

SYNOPSIS
      bal connector sdk analyze <sdk-ref> <output-dir>
               [sources=<path>] [include-packages=<packages>]
               [exclude-packages=<packages>] [max-depth=<n>]
               [methods-to-list=<n>] [include-deprecated]
               [include-internal] [include-non-public]

      bal connector sdk pipeline <dataset-key> <output-dir>
               [--fix-iterations=<n>] [--fix-code] [--fix-report-only]
               [--skip-fix] [--skip-tests]
               [--generate-examples|--skip-examples]
               [--generate-docs|--skip-docs]

      bal connector sdk generate <output-dir> [no-thinking]

      bal connector sdk connector <output-dir>

      bal connector sdk fix-code <output-dir> [--fix-iterations=<n>]

      bal connector sdk fix-report-only <output-dir> [--fix-iterations=<n>]

      bal connector sdk generate-tests <output-dir>

      bal connector sdk generate-examples <output-dir>

      bal connector sdk generate-docs <output-dir>

DESCRIPTION
       Analyze Java SDKs, generate API specifications and intermediate
       representations, generate Ballerina connector code, and optionally run
       AI-assisted code fixing, test generation, example generation, and
       documentation generation.

COMMANDS
       analyze
             Analyze a Java SDK from a dataset key or Maven coordinate and
             write SDK metadata under the output root.

       pipeline
             Run the full Java SDK connector workflow.

       generate
             Generate the API specification and intermediate representation
             from SDK analyzer metadata.

       connector
             Generate Ballerina connector artifacts from SDK metadata, IR, and
             API specification.

       fix-code
             Fix Java native adapter and Ballerina compilation errors in an
             SDK-generated connector.

       fix-report-only
             Run code fixer diagnostics for an SDK-generated connector without
             applying all fixes.

       generate-tests
             Generate live integration tests for an SDK-generated connector.

       generate-examples
             Generate AI-assisted Ballerina examples for an SDK-generated
             connector.

       generate-docs
             Generate all README documentation for an SDK-generated connector.

OPTIONS
       sources=<path>
             Path to a sources JAR or extracted source directory.

       include-packages=<packages>
             Comma-separated Java packages to include during SDK analysis.

       exclude-packages=<packages>
             Comma-separated Java packages to exclude during SDK analysis.

       max-depth=<n>
             Maximum dependency traversal depth.

       methods-to-list=<n>
             Maximum number of SDK methods to list for analysis.

       --fix-iterations=<n>
             Maximum code fixer iterations. The default is `3`.

FLAGS
       include-deprecated
             Include deprecated SDK methods.

       include-internal
             Include SDK classes or methods that would otherwise be treated as
             internal.

       include-non-public
             Include non-public SDK classes or methods.

       no-thinking, --no-thinking
             Disable extended LLM reasoning mode during specification
             generation.

       --fix-code
             Run the full code fixing phase.

       --fix-report-only
             Run code fixer diagnostics without applying all fixes.

       --skip-fix
             Skip the code fixing phase.

       --skip-tests
             Skip SDK live test generation.

       --generate-examples, --skip-examples
             Run or skip example generation.

       --generate-docs, --skip-docs
             Run or skip documentation generation.

EXAMPLES
       Analyze a Java SDK using a Maven coordinate.
             $ bal connector sdk analyze com.example:example-sdk:1.2.3 ./out

       Run the full SDK connector workflow.
             $ bal connector sdk pipeline example-sdk ./out --fix-iterations=3
